Class AbstractMRHBasePlugin<ReturnType>

java.lang.Object
  com.github.seqware.queryengine.plugins.hbasemr.AbstractMRHBasePlugin<ReturnType>

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class AbstractMRHBasePlugin<ReturnType>
extends Object
implements MapReducePlugin<Feature,FeatureSet>

Abstract implementation of an abstract map/reduce-based plug-in for a HBase back-end. Have not figured out how to reconcile an interface that defines map/reduce operations with the HBase map/reduce signatures.
